Description: Foot and lower wall fragment of small East Greek pottery closed vase; flaring button foot; inside and underside reserved, outside glazed; red dipinto under foot.
Bibliographic references: Johnston 2006a / Trademarks on Greek Vases: Addenda (East Greek 228, pl. 48.)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GM.43)
